a big game from junior Scott Fields, who scored on a 49-yard run. 
</P>
<P>
Santa Monica St. Monica 7, Van Nuys Montclair Prep 6 -- A failed point-after 
attempt was the difference as the Mariners defeated the Mounties at Culver City 
High. 
</P>
<P>
Trailing 7-0, Montclair Prep (0-2) scored with 2:49 left. 
</P>
