<DATELINE>
<P>
Boise, Idaho 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Boise Cascade Corp. has agreed to sell its Vancouver, Wash. paper million the 
first major step toward dramatically reducing its Pacific Northwest pulp and 
