PETER SELLARS' REMARK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I was appalled when I read "The Artist at the Helm" (Aug. 31), which was about 
Los Angeles Festival Director Peter Sellars. 
</P>
<P>
That a public figure would say "it doesn't make you look like a low-IQ retard" 
