opener against perennial power Santa Ana in the featured game in Orange County 
at 7:30 tonight in Placentia's Bradford Stadium. 
</P>
<P>
Esperanza, ranked third in The Times' preseason poll, has six returning 
starters on offense, including third-year quarterback Keith McDonald. 
</P>
<P>
