HOLMES REPLACES SCHAAF AT SANTA MARGARITA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Richard Schaaf has resigned as boys' basketball coach at Santa Margarita High 
School. 
</P>
<P>
He will be replaced by Roger Holmes, his assistant last season. 
</P>
<P>
Schaaf, who guided the Eagles to a 14-13 record last season, will remain as the 
school's athletic director. Holmes has named Todd Dixon as assistant coach. 
